name: The Strange Lab
description:
Investigate a strange lab, where scientist Dr Julia Rowley has gone missing!

Search for clues and try to piece together what happened to the doctor, and why she stole millions of funding just to seal herself away in a tiny lab.

You may only be able to find some clues by returning to different locations once you've interacted with others so keep searching! I'll eventually post a guide on how to get to the end and any additional extras you can find!
